data.description: Wonderful, Waterfront Ranch with Full, Finished Lower Level Walk-Out!!!  Over 3,000 SQ FT of Quality Features in this 5 bedroom, 3 Full Bath  Home on Private Hawk Lake!!! Panoramic Views & Plenty of Space for Family Gatherings on the Open-Concept Main Floor with Eat-In-Kitchen, Formal Living & Dining Rooms & New Composite Deck!  The Spacious Lower Level was Designed for Entertaining by Opening to the Covered Patio w/Stone Walkway to Your Own Private Dock!!! Gorgeous Views, Generous Room Sizes & Great Outdoor Amenities, without HOA Fees!!!  Newly Updated with Luxury Laminate Flooring & New Bedroom Carpeting on Main Level, as well as, New Kitchen Appliances & HW Heater.  Too Many Features to List!!!  Savvy Sellers Priced This Home to Sell!!!
